data.eml:eml: Checklist of the Acanthocephala in wildlife vertebrates of Mexico

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article García-Prieto, Luis, Garcia-Varela, Martín, Mendoza-Garfias, Berenit, León, Gerardo Pérez-Ponce De (2010): Checklist of the Acanthocephala in wildlife vertebrates of Mexico. Zootaxa 2419: 1-50, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.293878
